title: Second Chance
body: ****hi im very sad on my birthday because i though i would had a newly minted nft in my possession, but i must have made a mistake.  i bought 12 generation 0  bunnies and joined a sqad. but i must have transferred my cake after i pushed the button. i have really bad adhd and i guess i didn't read the instructions correctly. my suggestion is please allow for mistakes and give people a second chance to get it right. i would love to help.
